data.description: This villa  boasts an extended capri model, offering more space than others, plus an oversized lot for unmatched privacy. Enjoy sipping your morning coffee surrounded by lush greenery & the gentle Florida breeze. It's your very own piece of paradise!      Meticulously cared for, it features crown molding, plantation shutters, quartz countertops, new faucets throughout the home, along with many modern upgrades. The kitchen shines with quartz, new faucet, and dishwasher. Main bathroom offers renovated shower and quartz counters, while the guest bathroom impresses with black quartz. New laminate flooring graces the den area.  Newly painted garage floor!  Island Walk provides a resort-like experience with everything from   tennis on one of the 8 well-lit Har-tru courts, cool off in one of the two refreshing community pools, or relish the convenience of the on-site restaurant. State of the art fitness center!     1 YEAR HOME WARRANTY BEING OFFERED & $1400.00 CREDIT* FROM LENDER ASK FOR DETAILS
